The paper proposes a new approach to program analysis using deep learning, which involves building program vector representations. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Software Engineering (cs.SE) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses the advantages of deep learning, which suggests that it could also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of the coding criterion, which is related to programming languages (cs.PL), and the evaluation of the approach in terms of accuracy (cs.CR).
